my spirit is all the time.

18
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:28,431
Especially mornings.

19
00:02:28,498 --> 00:02:30,968
Tell you what: at lunch today,
I'm gonna buy you

20
00:02:31,034 --> 00:02:32,736
