it'll be a piece of cake.

24
00:02:40,544 --> 00:02:42,479
Ah, that's right.

25
00:02:42,546 --> 00:02:47,050
[bell tolls hour]

26
00:02:47,117 --> 00:02:48,752
[whoosh!]

27
00:02:48,819 --> 00:02:50,621
[muffled moaning, clatter]

28
00:02:50,688 --> 00:02:52,155
[Yu groans]

29
00:02:58,962 --> 00:03:00,063
