worry about me.

34
00:03:11,742 --> 00:03:14,745
[Yu] <i>His ability</i>
<i>is way too half‐assed.</i>

35
00:03:19,517 --> 00:03:24,855
<i>Ahhh! A flood of spices.</i>
<i>This is how curry should be!</i>
<i>Delicious!</i>

36
