must have been pretty desperate

72
00:05:23,273 --> 00:05:25,475
‐when they passed through here.
‐How's that?

73
00:05:25,543 --> 00:05:27,845
[Tomori] This side of the box
has no dust on it.

74
00:05:27,911 --> 00:05:31,582
In other words, whoever it was
ran through here
and bumped into this box.

75
00:05:31,649 --> 00:05:35,152
