an incident.

77
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:40,257
‐Another troublesome‐‐
‐For now we'll keep
moving forward.

78
00:05:43,293 --> 00:05:44,862
[Tomori] Two new sets
of footprints.

79
00:05:44,928 --> 00:05:46,496
