where an idol was being chased
by a big guy.

85
00:06:11,054 --> 00:06:13,624
‐[Tomori] An idol?
‐Let's see...

86
00:06:13,691 --> 00:06:15,926
Right, it was Yusa Nishimori.

87
00:06:15,993 --> 00:06:18,562
‐I've heard that name before.
‐[Yu] <i>Me too.</i>

88
00:06:18,629 --> 00:06:20,531
‐[fanfare plays]
‐Yusarin?!

89
00:06:20,598 --> 00:06:23,801
[Yu] <i>Oh, yeah.</i>
<i>It's the idol that Ayumi likes.</i>

90
00:06:23,867 --> 00:06:26,436
‐So you know her?
‐She's the unbelievable
lead vocalist

91
00:06:26,504 --> 00:06:28,939
for the band How‐Low‐Hello
and an upcoming gorgeous
super idol

92
00:06:29,006 --> 00:06:32,209
that sings and dances
like no one I've ever seen
in my life!

93
00:06:32,275 --> 00:06:34,912
I can't tell you what
a big turnoff that is. Stop!

94
00:06:34,978 --> 00:06:38,015
Her career started
in the sixth grade when
she won the grand prize

95
00:06:38,081 --> 00:06:40,751
in the 14th
reader‐model audition
for the magazine <i>Petit Banana</i>

96
00:06:40,818 --> 00:06:42,753
and debuted
as their exclusive model!

97
00:06:42,820 --> 00:06:47,057
Then she landed a job
as a regular member of
the "Movement Morning!" show

98
00:06:47,124 --> 00:06:49,159
