in show biz after‐‐

100
00:06:52,229 --> 00:06:53,764
Hold it.
Let's get back to the point.

101
00:06:53,831 --> 00:06:56,800
So that girl caused some issue
with her special ability

102
00:06:56,867 --> 00:06:58,902
