I'll chase him!

111
00:07:23,193 --> 00:07:26,630
‐[Yu] Tomori!
‐Otosaka, use your ability!

112
00:07:26,697 --> 00:07:27,831
[Yu] Huh?

113
00:07:27,898 --> 00:07:30,000
[energy pulses]

114
00:07:33,036 --> 00:07:34,538
[groans]

115
00:07:37,508 --> 00:07:38,976
[Yu moans]

116
00:07:39,042 --> 00:07:40,711
I'm the one who actually
feels the pain,

117
00:07:40,778 --> 00:07:43,947
so I'd rather you not
use this tactic from now on.

118
00:07:44,014 --> 00:07:46,984
‐This is why
we get compensation.
‐What?

119
00:07:47,050 --> 00:07:49,419
[groans] That hurt.

120
00:07:49,486 --> 00:07:52,556
Damn it, what would you have
done if the camcorder broke?

121
00:07:52,623 --> 00:07:53,991
