122
00:07:54,057 --> 00:07:56,126
[Tomori] Wake up, bastard.

123
00:07:56,193 --> 00:07:57,628
[suspect groans]

124
00:07:57,695 --> 00:07:59,663
[Tomori] Who the hell are you?

125
00:07:59,730 --> 00:08:01,431
No, who the hell are <i>you?</i>

126
00:08:01,498 --> 00:08:05,202
Tell us what we wanna know
and we'll call
an ambulance for you.

127
00:08:05,268 --> 00:08:08,105
You realize you're headed
straight to death right now?

128
00:08:08,171 --> 00:08:10,874
