have to film all this, do ya?

164
00:10:04,221 --> 00:10:06,123
[stranger] This way.
And don’t lag behind.

165
00:10:06,189 --> 00:10:08,025
Hey, I'm back.

166
00:10:08,091 --> 00:10:10,493
So how is everything
outside today?

167
00:10:12,329 --> 00:10:15,666
Ohh! It actually is
the real Yusarin!

168
00:10:15,733 --> 00:10:19,102
‐I have all
the How‐Low‐Hello CDs.
‐Big turnoff!

169
00:10:19,169 --> 00:10:21,471
Thanks so much,
that's wonderful.

170
00:10:21,539 --> 00:10:24,174
[Yu] <i>It really is</i>
<i>the girl I saw on TV.</i>

171
00:10:24,241 --> 00:10:26,076
Hey, what is with those guys?

172
00:10:26,143 --> 00:10:29,613
They're just like Misa
and have special abilities
that they can use.

173
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:33,517
Wait a minute, I thought
her name was Yusa,
but it's actually Misa?

174
00:10:33,584 --> 00:10:35,919
That's the part
that makes this complicated.

175
00:10:35,986 --> 00:10:38,756
What are you doing?
You sure we can trust them?

176
00:10:38,822 --> 00:10:41,892
I watched them use their powers
to defeat those other guys,
all right?

177
00:10:41,959 --> 00:10:45,062
Is it OK if we ask her directly
what's going on here?

178
00:10:45,128 --> 00:10:48,899
If you ask something stupid,
you're not getting out of here
in one piece.

179
00:10:48,966 --> 00:10:50,568
[Yu] <i>Why you gotta be so scary?</i>

180
00:10:50,634 --> 00:10:52,870
Tomori, be really careful here.

181
00:10:52,936 --> 00:10:54,471
Yeah, yeah.

182
00:10:54,538 --> 00:10:56,807
It's very nice to meet you.
I'm Tomori.

183
00:10:56,874 --> 00:11:01,044
I'm Yusa Nishimori,
nicknamed Yusarin.
It's very nice to meet <i>you.</i>

184
00:11:01,111 --> 00:11:03,480
[Yu] <i>So she</i>
<i>calls</i> herself <i>Yusarin?</i>

185
00:11:03,547 --> 00:11:05,916
This is the first time in
my life I've met a real idol.

186
00:11:05,983 --> 00:11:09,720
You're so unbelievably cute,
you almost look like a doll.

187
00:11:09,787 --> 00:11:12,656
‐I want to get as close
to you as she is.
‐Hey, back off!

188
00:11:12,723 --> 00:11:16,126
Now, now.
So first off, could you please
tell me your actual name?

189
00:11:16,193 --> 00:11:19,897
‐It's Yusa Kurobane.
‐Yeah? Well, I wasn't
asking you!

190
00:11:19,963 --> 00:11:22,465
