more like a stage name.

191
00:11:22,533 --> 00:11:24,367
Yes. I hear that a lot.

192
00:11:24,434 --> 00:11:26,369
But Kurobane means
"black feathers,"

193
00:11:26,436 --> 00:11:28,338
and it's not really suitable
for an idol,

194
00:11:28,405 --> 00:11:30,407
so they renamed me Nishimori.

195
00:11:30,473 --> 00:11:32,075
That makes sense.

196
00:11:32,142 --> 00:11:33,410
Now, there are some occasions

197
00:11:33,476 --> 00:11:35,278
when you are not
Yusa Kurobane.

198
00:11:35,345 --> 00:11:36,714
