199
00:11:36,780 --> 00:11:38,782
No, she's not, so how do you
know about it?

200
00:11:38,849 --> 00:11:41,619
‐I wasn't asking you, bastard.
‐What was that?

201
00:11:41,685 --> 00:11:43,587
So, was I right about that,
Kurobane?

202
00:11:43,654 --> 00:11:46,924
That's exactly it.
I guess you can call it
sleepwalking.

203
00:11:46,990 --> 00:11:49,226
I've been falling asleep
without realizing it,

204
00:11:49,292 --> 00:11:53,196
and then when I wake up,
I'm somewhere else,
with no idea how I got there.

205
00:11:53,263 --> 00:11:56,133
The doctors who examined me
said there's a chance
that I have

206
00:11:56,199 --> 00:11:57,334
a multiple personality disorder.

207
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:59,269
Oh, they did, huh?

208
00:11:59,336 --> 00:12:04,241
Well, it's not schizophrenia,
so you don't have to worry
about that.

209
00:12:04,307 --> 00:12:06,443
[sighs]

210
00:12:12,049 --> 00:12:15,085
She has her own special ability
just like the three of us.

211
00:12:15,152 --> 00:12:18,589
Her power is
to allow a dead person
to possess her body.

212
00:12:18,656 --> 00:12:20,023
