were talking about earlier.

215
00:12:25,529 --> 00:12:27,565
‐[Yusa] Misa?
‐[Tomori] Is something
the matter?

216
00:12:27,631 --> 00:12:31,301
‐[Kota] Don't ask anything.
‐Is it someone she knew?

217
00:12:31,368 --> 00:12:33,537
Yeah, she was Yusa's
older sister.

218
00:12:33,604 --> 00:12:36,907
