in an accident.

219
00:12:38,075 --> 00:12:39,643
You bastard.

220
00:12:39,710 --> 00:12:41,545
Don't go blabbing on
about things

221
00:12:41,612 --> 00:12:44,314
to some stranger
you just met!

222
00:12:44,381 --> 00:12:47,084
‐[Takajo groans]
‐Can I assume that you're Misa?

223
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:51,021
It's so annoying how cramped
it is with all of you here!

224
00:12:51,088 --> 00:12:53,323
[Yu]
<i>She’s totally changed.</i>

225
00:12:58,495 --> 00:13:01,098
‐[Tomori]
‐Whoa, that's really impressive.

226
00:13:01,164 --> 00:13:05,669
[Sho] Calm down, Misa!
You're gonna burn us all
to death!

227
00:13:08,606 --> 00:13:11,775
